<br>
2nd box is me getting hit, and how much I am hitting for.  Everyone else's hits are off, my pet hammer's hits are off, honestly I could turn my own hits off.  Chat channels 1 and 2 are in there.  I dunno.  Probably not the most efficient setup, but it works for me.<br>
<br>
Spells are horizontal along the top of the screen, chat at the bottom, target menu on top of the chat menus, hotkeys to the right, left side is all group health menus and so forth, between the chats and the health menus is the spell bar, I click them or use hotkeys rather than Alt4 or whatever.  I'm used to it.  I do pretty well at me job, I think.  I could play somebody else's setup and probably kill everyone.  heh.<br>
